name: Pushingo
overview: -Original Story: The princess is in danger! You are the only one who can save her. A cute logical game for kids. -Controls on original machine: Start the game/Restart the level: Start Move: Cursor Keys Push: A This is a homebrought game, run on Gameboy Pocket. A game by: László Rajcsányi - Wilds, 2021. Created with GB-Studio 2.0.0-beta5 by Chris Maltby! This game is an entry for the Gameboy Competition 2021.
